##### RURIKOVICH

## MASSALSKY 1010064
# https://www.angelfire.com/realm/gotha/gotha/massalsky.html

# Pr Karachevsky Svyatoslav Titovich and Theodora, daughter of the Lithuanian prince Olgerd
	# Pr Yuri Svyatoslavovich Karachevsky (XV tribe from Rurik 
	# who lived in the second half of the 15th century , received from his father the city of Mosalsk as an inheritance and became the first specific prince of Mosalsky (one of the Upper Oka principalities ).
		# Pr Vladimir Yurievich
			# ...
				# Prince Athanasius-Vladislav was taken prisoner at the beginning of the 18th century and remained in Russia with his offspring.
		# Vasily Yuryevich
			# x
				# Mikhail
					# Vasily Mikhailovich Mosalsky
						# Litvinov-Mosalsky, Vasily Vasilievich						-->		Litvinov-Mosalsky
					# Prince Semyon Mikhailovich Mosalsky
						# Vasily Semyonovich Mosalsky , nicknamed "Koltso" (+1577)  -->		Koltsov-Mosalsky
						# Andrei
						# Roman
						# Pyotr
		# Semyon Yuryevich
			# Ivan
				# 	
				# Semyon
			# x
				# x
					# Pr Ivan Dmitrievich Klubok, who also crossed from Lithuania to Russia, became the ancestor of the branch of the Klubkov-Mosalsky princes , which died out in the first half of the 17th century

# Владислав-Афанасий a descendant of Prince Vladimir Yuryevich, moved from the Principality of Lithuania to Russia at the beginning of the 18th century. This branch of the Mosalsky princes lost their princely title. In 1862, the princely title was returned to the descendants of D. A. Masalsky
	# Даниил (Данило) Афанасьевич Масальский (December 18, 1739-November 13, 1832); m.Maria Efimovna Pozharskaya (1754-1827) he had 17 children
